track_notes: Parking at the small gravel parking place at the end of the road. Continue up the valley. When you reach the red hiking trail, continue left up the gravel logging road instead. Zig-zag up the mountain following the road and directly up the steep hill trough the clearing. Then follow the ridge to the summit. Descent to the saddle on the other side and then take sharp right down the clearing and descend to a logging road. Follow the logging road back, it is much more comfortable than re-tracking the ascent route.
